logika sederhana: 

jika absen masuk = 1
jika absen keluar = 1

value awal sebelum absen = 0





--------------------------------------------
jam   | absen_masuk | absen keluar
-------------------------------------------- --> jika absen masuk
07.00 |     1		| 		0
-------------------------------------------- --> jika absen keluar (update)
05.00 | 	1		| 		1
--------------------------------------------